{
  "texts": [
    "This approach was particularly effective in helping students grasp challenging topics and sustain steady progress in their learning journeys (Kılınç, 2023; Tran, 2024).",
    "However, some students identified limitations inherent to ChatGPT, specifically its inability to offer the same level of nuanced support as a human tutor.",
    "While the bot effectively provides immediate assistance and personalized responses, it lacks the depth and flexibility required for more advanced PL needs (Dalgıç et al., 2024).",
    "Overall, students considered ChatGPT a valuable supplementary tool, underscoring the necessity for symbiotic integration with human educators to enhance effectiveness in PL contexts (Mohebi, 2024).",
    "In this study, we implemented a specific learning process to engage learners in conversations with a ChatGPT-based tutor bot and examined the interactions as well as students' perceptions of the bot's effectiveness in promoting PL and facilitating the acquisition of new knowledge."
  ]
}